{
  "text": "At the clinical level, the identification of new variants is not routinely requested because pharmaco genetic studies require deeper clinical validation of genetic information with larger case series and functional in vitro evaluation of variants before the inclusion into clinical practice [CITATION_1] . Nevertheless, the possibility to constantly implement new putative multimarker findings into the analysis must not be excluded.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "8714945"
